      "span_text": "The R package edgeR [CITATION_2] ) that estimate expected variance in gene expression from a negative binomial distribution and uses a generalized linear model to identify differentially expressed genes were employed to detect genes that have a different level of gene expression in testes from fish subjected to 1.2 ng/L or 1.6 ng/L of EE 2 compared with unexposed fish."
